giri kanye ( kannada : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is a 1977 indian kannada drama film directed by dorai - bhagwan duo . it is based on the novel of the same name by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . the film stars rajkumar , jayamala and vajramuni in lead roles . the film was a musical blockbuster with all the songs composed by rajan-nagendra considered evergreen hits . rajinikanth was initially selected to play the villain 's role which was eventually played by thoogudeepa srinivas .